title: WisdomTree U.S. MidCap Dividend Fund (DON) Shares Cross Above 200 DMA - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the WisdomTree U.S. MidCap Dividend Fund ETF (Symbol: DON) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $35.15, changing hands as high as $35.52 per share.
